    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** [x \u2193 F] is a coslice category; [F \u2193 x] is a slice category; [x \u2193 F] deals with morphisms [x -> F y]; [F \u2193 x] has morphisms [F y -> x] *)\n"
